# 🚀 Smart Resource Allocation — Execution Plan

## **Project: Data-Driven Volunteer Coordination for Social Impact**

> **Codename:** `PromptWars` | **Hackathon Duration:** 48 Hours

---

## 1. Project Vision (30-Second Elevator Pitch)

> *"NGOs drown in paper. Volunteers sit idle. People suffer waiting. Our platform digitizes scattered field data with OCR, visualizes community needs on a real-time crisis map, and uses a smart matching algorithm to instantly deploy the right volunteer to the right place — cutting response time from days to minutes."*

---

