---

## 3. Tech Stack (Final)

| Layer | Technology | Why? |
|-------|-----------|------|
| **Frontend** | React 18 + Vite | Fast dev, hot reload, component-based |
| **Styling** | Vanilla CSS + CSS Variables | Full control, no dependency bloat |
| **Maps** | Leaflet.js + OpenStreetMap | Free, no API key needed, great for hackathons |
| **OCR** | Tesseract.js (browser-side) | No server cost, runs in-browser, instant demo |
| **Backend** | Python + FastAPI | Blazing fast, auto-docs (Swagger), async support |
| **Database** | MongoDB (via Motor - async) | Schema-flexible for varied survey data |
| **Auth** | JWT (simple token-based) | Lightweight, hackathon-appropriate |
| **Notifications** | Browser Push API / Toast UI | Simple, no third-party dependency |
| **Deployment** | Render (Backend) + Vercel (Frontend) | Free tier, instant deploy |

---

## 4. Feature Breakdown & Priority

### 🔴 P0 — Must Have (Core Demo)

| # | Feature | Description |
|---|---------|-------------|
| 1 | **Need Reporting Form** | Volunteers submit community needs (category, location, urgency, description) |
| 2 | **Crisis Map Dashboard** | Interactive Leaflet map showing all needs as color-coded markers |
| 3 | **Volunteer Registration** | Sign up with skills, location (auto-detect GPS), availability |
| 4 | **Smart Matching Algorithm** | Auto-assign nearest + most-skilled + available volunteer to a need |
| 5 | **OCR Survey Upload** | Upload paper survey photo → extract text → auto-fill need form |
| 6 | **Task Assignment Panel** | Admin can view matches, approve/override, track status |

### 🟡 P1 — Should Have (Polish)

| # | Feature | Description |
|---|---------|-------------|
| 7 | **Filters & Search** | Filter map by category (Medical, Food, Shelter), urgency level |
| 8 | **Volunteer Status Tracking** | Assigned / En Route / Completed status flow |
| 9 | **Analytics Dashboard** | Charts showing needs by category, response times, regional heatmap |
| 10 | **Real-time Notifications** | Toast/push alerts when volunteer gets assigned a task |

### 🟢 P2 — Nice to Have (Wow Factor)

| # | Feature | Description |
|---|---------|-------------|
| 11 | **NLP Auto-Categorization** | Auto-detect need category from free-text description |
| 12 | **Urgency Scoring AI** | Auto-score urgency 1-5 based on keywords |
| 13 | **Route Optimization** | Show best route for volunteer to reach the need location |
| 14 | **Multi-language OCR** | Hindi + English paper survey support |

