## 6. API Design (FastAPI Endpoints)

### Auth
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/auth/register` | Register volunteer/admin |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/login` | Login → JWT token |
| `GET` | `/api/auth/me` | Get current user profile |

### Needs
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/needs` | Report a new community need |
| `GET` | `/api/needs` | List all needs (with filters: category, urgency, status) |
| `GET` | `/api/needs/:id` | Get single need detail |
| `PATCH` | `/api/needs/:id` | Update need status |
| `DELETE` | `/api/needs/:id` | Remove a need (admin only) |

### Volunteers
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/api/volunteers` | List all volunteers (with filters) |
| `PATCH` | `/api/volunteers/:id/availability` | Update availability status |
| `GET` | `/api/volunteers/:id/tasks` | Get volunteer's task history |

### Matching
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/match/:need_id` | Trigger smart matching for a specific need |
| `GET` | `/api/match/suggestions/:need_id` | Get top 5 volunteer suggestions |
| `POST` | `/api/assignments` | Confirm assignment |
| `PATCH` | `/api/assignments/:id/status` | Update: accepted → in_progress → completed |

### OCR
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/ocr/extract` | Upload image → return extracted text (client-side Tesseract fallback) |

### Analytics
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/api/analytics/summary` | Total needs, volunteers, response time stats |
| `GET` | `/api/analytics/heatmap` | Geo-clustered need density data |

